 # Role-Based Access Control
 
-https://help.cardinalapps.io/guides/cardinal-media-server/role-based-access-control
+## Core Design
+
+The design of the RBAC layer is built on two concepts: Capabilities and Roles.
+These concepts are documented in detail on the public Help Site page for the
+Media Server.
